			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002321_0001"/><!--pb/@n='73r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">1<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> June 1865</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>Oswell</persName> sent the 
<lb/>sentence, which was 
<lb/>proposed, to me, &amp; 
<lb/>I have added it to 
<lb/>the dedication - I 
<lb/>suppose the named 
<lb/>need not be added to 
<lb/>the preface<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I have written 
<lb/>to <persName>Madame Hocédé</persName>
<lb/>today.</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Murchison</persName> let 
<lb/>the cat out of the 
<lb/>bag that <persName>Young</persName>
<lb/>gave the thousand 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002321_0002"/><!--pb/@n='73v'-->
<lb/>by printing it in his 
<lb/>address.</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">David Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p>I wrote to <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Charles 
<lb/>Livingstone</persName> yesterday 
<lb/>to say that the 
<lb/>publication was 
<lb/>stopped till Nov<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi><reg>.</reg></p>
			
</div>
